12:05:28 | <span class="text-purple-400">SENSOR</span> | imu-driver:read()   832 bytes
<span class="text-rose-400 font-semibold">12:06:51 | !!! TAMPER ALERT !!!</span>
         | FILE   | /models/detect.pb   <span class="text-rose-400 font-semibold">hash mismatch</span>
         | expected 5f12…4c31, got a97c…b11e
